<!DOCTYPE html> <html lang="en"> <head>   <meta charset="UTF-8">   <title>Feature Information</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>    body { background-color: #f8f9fa; }    .card { border-radius: 8px; }  </style>
</head> <body> <div class="container mt-4">
  <div class="card p-4">    <h4 class="mb-3">Feature Information</h4>
    <hr>
    <h5>UCI Student Performance Dataset Features</h5>
    <h3>G1 (1st period grade )</h3>    <p>    First period grade (numeric: from 0 to 20).    </p>
    <h3>G2 (2nd period grade)</h3>    <p>    Second period grade (numeric: from 0 to 20).    </p>
    <h3>G3 (final grade)</h3>    <p>    Final grade (numeric: from 0 to 20).    </p>
    <h3>Absences</h3>    <p>    Number of school absences (numeric: from 0 to 93).    </p>
    <h3>Study time</h3>    <p>    Weekly study time (numeric: 1 - <2 hours; 2 - 2 to 5 hours; 3 - 5 to 10 hours; 4 - >10 hours).    </p>
    <hr>
    <h5>MOOC Student Activity Features</h5>
    <h3>Registered</h3>    <p>    Indicates if the student is registered for the course.    </p>
    <h3>Viewed</h3>    <p>    Total number of course content views.    </p>
    <h3>Explored</h3>    <p>    Total number of course chapters explored.    </p>
    <h3>Nevents</h3>    <p>    Total number of events (clicks, interactions) on the platform.    </p>
    <h3>Ndays_act</h3>    <p>    Number of days the student was active in the course.    </p>
    <h3>Nplay_video</h3>    <p>    Total number of video plays.    </p>
    <h3>Nchapters</h3>    <p>    Number of chapters accessed.    </p>
    <h3>Nforum_posts</h3>    <p>    Number of posts made in the course forum.    </p>
    <h3>Incomplete</h3>    <p>    Flag indicating an incomplete course status.    </p>
    <h3>Year of Birth (YoB)</h3>    <p>    Student's year of birth.    </p>
    <hr>
    <h5>Questionnaire Student Demographic Features</h5>
    <h3>Marital status</h3>    <p>    Encoded marital status of the student.    </p>
    <h3>Application mode</h3>    <p>    Encoded method of application to the institution.    </p>
    <h3>Course</h3>    <p>    Encoded identifier of the enrolled academic program.    </p>
    <h3>Daytime / Evening attendance</h3>    <p>    Indicates whether the student attends daytime or evening classes.    </p>
    <h3>Previous qualification</h3>    <p>    Highest level of education completed before enrollment.    </p>
    <h3>Nationality</h3>    <p>    Encoded nationality of the student.    </p>
    <h3>Mother’s qualification</h3>    <p>    Encoded education level of the student’s mother.    </p>
    <h3>Father’s qualification</h3>    <p>    Encoded education level of the student’s father.    </p>
    <h3>Mother’s occupation</h3>    <p>    Encoded employment category of the student’s mother.    </p>
    <h3>Father’s occupation</h3>    <p>    Encoded employment category of the student’s father.    </p>
    <h3>Displaced</h3>    <p>    Indicates whether the student is classified as displaced.    </p>
    <h3>Educational special needs</h3>    <p>    Indicates whether the student has special educational requirements.    </p>
    <h3>Debtor</h3>    <p>    Indicates whether the student has outstanding tuition debt.    </p>
    <h3>Tuition fees up to date</h3>    <p>    Indicates whether tuition payments are fully paid.    </p>
    <h3>Gender</h3>    <p>    Encoded gender of the student.    </p>
    <h3>Scholarship holder</h3>    <p>    Indicates whether the student receives financial aid.    </p>
    <h3>Age at enrollment</h3>    <p>    Student’s age at the time of enrollment.    </p>
    <h3>International</h3>    <p>    Indicates whether the student is an international student.    </p>
    <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-primary mt-3">← Back</a>  </div>
</div> </body> </html> 
